00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.000
Question three: Cloudy day or office hours—what’s the best move?

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:17.000
Consider whether brief time outdoors beats window light.

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:26.000
Coaching: glass filters brightness; even two minutes outside can help the brain register daylight.

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:35.000
Barrier coach: link it to coffee, a voice memo, or a quick call—one cue, two wins.

